BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Meetup: Shut Up & Write Wine Country
X-SOURCE-URL:https://www.meetup.com/shutupandwritewinecountry/
UID:event_313546096@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260317T163535Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260318T130000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260318T143000
SUMMARY:Shut Up & Write!® Sebastopol: In Person
DESCRIPTION:Shut Up & Write!® Wine Country\nJoin us for an hour of writin
 g! Any kind of writing\, including a novel\, blog\, script\, dissertation\
 , melody\, poem\, memoir\, etc. No one will see what you've written or giv
 e unsolicited advice. Try it out at 1:00 PM on Wednesday afternoons.\n\nSC
 HEDULE:\n\n1:00-1:15: Introductions\n\n1:15-2:15: Write in silence for 1 h
 our\n\n2:15-2:30: Check-ins: how did it go?\n\nDetails:\n\n\\- Wifi: Coffe
 e & Moore has wifi\\. Password: goodcoffee\n\n\\- Parking: This location h
 as a parking lot\\.\n\n\\- Patronage: Please thank our hosts by purchasing
  something\\.\n\n\\- Outlets: Scattered around if you need to charge your 
 laptop\\.\n\n\\- Noise: Some writers use headphones or earplugs to block a
 mbient noise\\.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/shutupandwritewinecountry/events/3135
 46096/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260226T214006Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260226T214006Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Meetup: Shut Up & Write Wine Country
X-SOURCE-URL:https://www.meetup.com/shutupandwritewinecountry/
UID:event_313561368@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260317T163535Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260319T100000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260319T120000
SUMMARY:Shut Up & Write!® at Redwood Café in Cotati (in person)
DESCRIPTION:Shut Up & Write!® Wine Country\n**Coworking for writers in Co
 tati!**\nJoin us for some focused writing time. All experience levels are 
 welcome\, and don’t worry\, no one will see what you've written. This se
 ssion is about WRITING\, whether you're working on a novel\, memoir\, play
 \, short story\, dissertation\, job application\, blog\, poetry\, journal\
 , or song.\n\n**Format**\n10:00 - 10:15 AM: Introduce yourself and what yo
 u're working on today\n10:15 - 11:30 AM: Write in silence for 1 hour and 1
 5 minutes.\n11:30 - 11:45 AM: Check in with one another and share how it w
 ent\n\n**Venue Details:**\n\n* Redwood Cafe has WiFi for guests\n* Ample s
 treet parking is available\n* Please thank our hosts by purchasing somethi
 ng\n* If music or ambient noise are distracting\, please bring ear plugs o
 r headphones\n* Outlets are available if you need to charge your laptop
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/shutupandwritewinecountry/events/3135
 61368/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260227T193112Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260227T193112Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Meetup: Shut Up & Write Wine Country
X-SOURCE-URL:https://www.meetup.com/shutupandwritewinecountry/
UID:event_313578916@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260317T163535Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260320T150000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260320T163000
SUMMARY:Shut Up & Write!™ Santa Rosa REMOTE ZOOM FRIDAY 
DESCRIPTION:Shut Up & Write!® Wine Country\n**This event is hosted on the
  Shut Up & Write website\, so please [sign up here](https://shutupwrite.co
 m/series/shut-up-write-online-with-lorraine-s/7480) for your writing event
 .**\n\n**ABOUT THE EVENT**\nWelcome! I will email passcode to those who re
 gister.\nBe sure to enable email on MeetUp!\nThen\, please check your emai
 l!\nJoin us virtually for an hour + of writing using Zoom. Let's keep toge
 ther as much as we can during these uncertain times and keep on writing. L
 ook for the schedule online and join us.\n\nWe’ve discovered that it’s
  strikingly helpful to write with other writers. See if it’s true for yo
 u at 3pm on Friday afternoon. Be it a book\, blog\, script\, essay\, disse
 rtation\, resume\, melody\, poem or just plain work stuff\, you are invite
 d to write it with us. No one will see what you've written or give you uns
 olicited advice. Instead of just thinking about writing\, come and get som
 e real writing done.\n\nJOIN US!\n\n1. RSVP - space is limited to 12 peopl
 e. (registration closes at one half hour before the event starts). You wil
 l receive the link to access the event at that time. REMEMBER TO CHECK YOU
 R EMAIL FOR PASSCODE!\n2. Before or at 3pm join the meeting with the link 
 you receive AND ADD PASSCODE.\n\nPlease note:\n\n1. If you don't have Zoom
  set up on your computer yet\, leave 15-30 minutes ahead of time to get it
  set up!\n2. If you have difficulty with audio (don't have a microphone se
 t up)\, as long as you have a speaker\, you can call in (you'll see phone 
 numbers when you log in).\n3. If you are late\, you won't be able to intro
  with us\, but you are still welcome to join in.\n4. If you won't be able 
 to make it\, please cancel so that the space is available to another write
 r.\n\nSCHEDULE:\n3:00 - quick intros.\naround 3:10 - timer starts: write f
 or 70 mins.\n4:20 - (the end) wrap up\n\nWherever you are\, we hope to see
  you online! Keep on writing...\nRegards\,\nLorraine Segal
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/shutupandwritewinecountry/events/3135
 78916/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260228T232535Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260228T232535Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
